overview: It's a brand new semester for Ashlynn... which means new books, new classes, and new problems. This time around, she finds her bank account to be a little low, so she decides to make a little money! Whether she's a cable girl, pizza delivery girl, or a plumber, she does everything it takes to get the gig done. Oh man, she can work it like a part time job...literally.
tagline: No Cash... No Job... No Tuition... No Problem!
title: Ashlynn Goes to College 3
